      <!-- No subscription -->
      <section class="o-container  o-container--mw1100  u-py-72  u-text-monsoon">

        <div class="u-text-monsoon">

          <h2 class="c-section-heading  u-mb-24  u-text-mine-shaft  u-text-center  u-wf-700  u-ls-tightest">
            No subscription.
          </h2>

          <p class="c-section-subheading">
            Version 2 of the Affinity apps are available to buy with a one-time payment. This not only gets you the latest and greatest versions of Affinity, but you will also receive free updates (such as the recent 2.1 update) until such a time Version 3 is released!
          </p>

          <p class="c-section-subheading  u-mb-48">
            We offer incredibly flexible licensing options – either pick and choose which apps you want, or opt for the Universal Licence and get the whole suite on all platforms for one low price.
